events.body:
@gapeman Welcome!
Screenshots "before" and "after" are appreciated in the PR description.
Concept NACK because I think that the current icon does this job. Also we are using icons from [here](https://www.s-ings.com/typicons/) and I think its better to keep using these icons

Looks not to bad. Either we use an icon from https://www.s-ings.com/typicons/ or you would need to put an entry into `doc/assets-attribution.md` (creator, license, etc.).

However, I think your new icon would require padding to not appear overly large.

p.s. Updated copyright 2 times because I accidentally removed "< >" symbols

c95ad1d looks good, but please squash the commits

Would also be good to add a screenshot of the icon in context.
